<!-- pages/home/index.wxml — 选餐入口（v6 设计稿：品牌头 + 堂食/外卖分段 + 扫码卡 + 厨师 banner + 福利放送） -->
<view class="page home-page">

  <!-- 品牌头（品牌粉渐变）：字标 + 分段。不含余额/福利金。 -->
  <view class="home-hd">
    <view class="brandrow">
      <view class="logo">鸡</view>
      <view class="brandtext">
        <view class="brandname">鸡福旺</view>
        <view class="brandsub">五指毛桃鸡 · 现炸小食</view>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="seg">
      <view class="s {{mode === 'dine_in' ? 's_on' : ''}}" hover-class="seg_tap" bindtap="selectDineIn">
        <view class="seg-ic seg-ic_dine"></view>堂食点餐
      </view>
      <view class="s {{mode === 'delivery' ? 's_on' : ''}}" hover-class="seg_tap" bindtap="chooseDelivery">
        <view class="seg-ic seg-ic_deliver"></view>外卖到家
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <!-- 扫码点餐卡（堂食） -->
  <view class="scan" hover-class="scan_tap" hover-stay-time="120" bindtap="scanDineIn">
    <view class="scan-qr scan-qr-ic"></view>
    <view class="scan-tx">
      <view class="scan-t">扫码点餐</view>
      <view class="scan-d">扫描餐桌二维码，立即开点</view>
    </view>
    <view class="scan-go">›</view>
  </view>

  <!-- 现炸 banner（炸鸡插画） -->
  <view class="banner">
    <view class="banner-txt">
      <view class="banner-h">现炸出炉</view>
      <view class="banner-p">五指毛桃鸡 · 现点现做</view>
      <view class="banner-b" bindtap="scanDineIn">查看今日菜单</view>
    </view>
    <view class="home-hero"></view>
  </view>

  <!-- 人气推荐（静态装饰位，暂不接数据；日后可接精选菜品） -->
  <view class="sec-title">
    <view class="sec-h">人气推荐</view>
    <view class="sec-more">更多 ›</view>
  </view>
  <view class="promos">
    <view class="promo">
      <view class="promo-img warm1 promo-bowl"></view>
      <view class="promo-ct"><view class="promo-n">招牌窑鸡</view><view class="promo-pr">¥38<text class="promo-from">起</text></view></view>
    </view>
    <view class="promo">
      <view class="promo-img warm2 promo-greens"></view>
      <view class="promo-ct"><view class="promo-n">黄金鸡米花</view><view class="promo-pr">¥18<text class="promo-from">起</text></view></view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <!-- 底部 tabbar -->
  <view class="tabbar-fixed">
    <tabbar current="{{tabbarCurrent}}" bindchange="tabChange" />
  </view>
</view>
